===Runners-up===

* [[Senior Bowl (bridge)|d'Orsi Senior Bowl]] (2) 2009, 2013 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
